<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-27 13:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7515 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-DISTRACTED-DRIVERS-NY     05-27 0755
