<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-27 22:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7925 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s BC-BKN-MODESTI-COLUMN-LA     05-27 0870
